### Register a new Institution User and Institution Record
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register-institution
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ezHHKe@myschool.edu",
  "password": "strongPassword!123",
  "firstName": "Principal",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "name": "My Hard School",
  "address": "456 Learning Ave, Scholar Town, ST 12345",
  "contactEmail": "oiseeeerdkbe@myschool.edu"
}

### Register another institution (example with minimal data)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register-institution
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@anotherschool.org",
  "password": "anotherPassword#456",
  "name": "Another Fine School"
  // Address and contactEmail are optional in the service,
  // contactEmail will default to the user's email if not provided
}